=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/1066992/iphone-14-and-iphone-14-pro-best-carrier-and-store-deals.html\">iPhone 14 deals</a> and <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2073364/iphone-15-and-iphone-15-pro-best-deals-carriers-stores-online.html\">iPhone 15 deals for U.S. readers</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the U.K., we frequently see Apple-certified resellers discount unlocked iPhones. Right now we are seeing up to £100 off the price of most iPhone 15 handsets at several resellers currently: look for money off at <a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B0CHXFCYCR?tag=macworld05-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Amazon</a>, <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=1599&amp;awinaffid=254429&amp;clickref=1-1-541154-1-0-0&amp;ued=https://www.currys.co.uk/products/apple-iphone-15-128-gb-yellow-10254988.html\" target=\"_blank\">Currys</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=3090&amp;awinaffid=254429&amp;clickref=1-1-541154-1-0-0&amp;ued=https://www.very.co.uk/apple-iphone-15-256gb--nbspblue/1600930501.prd\" target=\"_blank\">Very</a>. We are recording all the <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2075192/iphone-15-plus-pro-max-best-deals-carriers-uk.html\">best prices of iPhone 15 in the U.K.</a> separately, but here is a small selection:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Amazon, <a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B0CHXFCYCR?tag=macworld05-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">iPhone 15, 128GB,</a> £699 (£100 off, RRP £799)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Amazon, <a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B0CHX9XRMN?tag=macworld05-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">iPhone 15 Plus, 128GB,</a> £799 (£100 off, RRP £899)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Amazon, <a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B0CHX53QY9?tag=macworld05-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">iPhone 15 Pro, 128GB</a>, £899 (£100 off, RRP £999)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Amazon, <a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.u